Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 是shin吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是你的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是晴天就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨看不见就没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不见 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:31.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢 出主意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 糟了 shin也往这里看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你说想看mineme流星群的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 先很好的敷衍过这个话题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 这个事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.87,0:07:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 还有什么其他的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.58,0:07:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一不下心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.02,0:07:54.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太不小心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甲信越的本周天气预报总体晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很期待啊 流星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我说了想看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你学习还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了没事了所以才去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来 kent 你是数学系的研究生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他教你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊 事先整理好要问的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可以不浪费时间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部到齐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.59,0:08:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此次目的在于
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.48,0:08:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让零度之羊的工作人员增加友谊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说了 那么 废话少说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家尽情的玩耍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算 撑过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 竟是不懂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 让大家觉得奇怪也无可奈可
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 要特别注意mine和shin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.74,0:09:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉她们已经起疑心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了，可以成为你记忆暗示的那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由你去主动问问或许更有效
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 要是能这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.85,0:09:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明说了会加油的 可是完全不够
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,orion在 我觉得很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么说 我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 怎么也找不回那些记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信号是红灯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发呆可是很危险的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也有过这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夷？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.22,0:10:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不记得我…了吗    也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 以前见过那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么感觉我刚才心绪不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好美的景色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我是第一次乘坐这个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.05,0:11:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 很不错的地方唉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 shin又在看你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么总感觉他好像说什么的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道　感觉到你失忆的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:58.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周末不是晴空万丈 降水率为0的吗？kent
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是半周的预报 天气瞬息万变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法的了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是倾盆大雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了，大家 我想这雨很快就停了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不见要停啊 你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过气味知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？气味？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气通过气味就能预测吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正不管怎么看 就是不见停啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说 即使是对我保证一件事情也好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,kent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约定了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.69,0:12:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 真像waka说的那样 雨真停了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚说完就停了 真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:06.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨的味道 是什么样的味道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.08,0:13:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 我的脸上沾上什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的表情像在做白日梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.19,0:13:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 他这么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 问一下他 你看到的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:33.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那个 听见雨的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会想起之前去过的庙会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,许多漂亮的风铃摆在摊子上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下小雨的时候 kent把我拉到伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.01,0:13:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  又是面无表情 记得吗 记不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你 去庙会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么看来 kent这好像没有线索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.91,0:14:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 唉 到现在为止你看到的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.65,0:14:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是片段 连接不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现的人也是乱七八糟 到底是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:23.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 因为是失忆之前经历的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 一边等流星 一边一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团体赛 台式冰球开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.51,0:14:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 最先的对决shin&toma队 对 kent&Ikki队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,shin 你防我守 这样可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 除此之外没有更好的布局了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有人大声说出了作战计划了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不起我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.65,0:15:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有呢  Ikki 很擅长这个游戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是乒乓球部的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 是飞镖部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊 动手的游戏都很擅长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.09,0:15:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不需要作战会议吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.06,0:15:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经决定了 我立案 Ikiki 实施
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.26,0:15:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ikiki 不会是 ikki吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绰号 真名 无论哪个 都不合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上干活的不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的好随意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 俩对准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛开始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:15:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故意露破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,kent&Ikki 队胜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说 Ikki 也太强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 kent的大胆的作战计划也相当了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 动手的游戏没胜算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 打牌 玩扑克吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.14,0:16:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 不过 先说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是无论什么动手的游戏都很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扑克也是 另一种意思的动手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 已经 觉得不会赢Ikki
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 来了真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.68,0:16:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 谢谢 orion
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 我什么也没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我一个人的话 肯定不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有orion在 帮了我很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 太好了 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是和你在一起 很快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这样一来 就和你一起有许多的经历 很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,orion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 下一个就轮到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.13,0:17:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,E打得落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,mineme流星群 据说看到这个流星群的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会在心里留下美好的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望今晚留下好的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长 还有多远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.85,0:17:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才就这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:17:58.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,台式冰球太卖力了 用光了力气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.33,0:18:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 多亏了你赢了那个店长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我自己也吓了一跳
